- In "My Love from the Star,"

537
00:18:01,961 --> 00:18:03,930
I played a sociopath,

538
00:18:03,931 --> 00:18:05,200
- Right.
- which drew a lot of attention.

539
00:18:05,201 --> 00:18:06,301
That character is a total scumbag.

540
00:18:06,401 --> 00:18:09,900
Back then, you had some noticeable stubble.

541
00:18:09,901 --> 00:18:11,871
- And your lips are so red.
- Back then, my stubble was showing.

542
00:18:12,041 --> 00:18:14,210
