- Yes, I did.

543
00:18:14,211 --> 00:18:16,410
- So did I. It's really good.
- Indeed.

544
00:18:16,411 --> 00:18:18,211
- Your skin gets irritated...
- Yeong Cheol did that too?

545
00:18:18,381 --> 00:18:19,850
