- Yes.

546
00:18:19,851 --> 00:18:20,980
I don't have to worry about it anymore.

547
00:18:20,981 --> 00:18:23,721
No one in the whole country would want to know if you had it removed.

548
00:18:24,151 --> 00:18:25,220
Gosh, seriously.

549
00:18:25,221 --> 00:18:26,991
Not a single person in the whole world...

550
