So I went through ten laser hair removal treatments.

553
00:18:34,731 --> 00:18:35,890
And I don't shave anymore.

554
00:18:35,891 --> 00:18:37,130
- It's clean.
- Really?

555
00:18:37,131 --> 00:18:38,501
No, it's not clean.

556
00:18:38,701 --> 00:18:41,301
Who wants to know you went through ten sessions?

557
00:18:41,571 --> 00:18:43,271
- I actually have two sessions left.
- He also...

558
00:18:43,401 --> 00:18:46,040
- Why didn't you grow it instead?
- When you talk using the app...

559
00:18:46,041 --> 00:18:47,371
- Are we talking...
- Those who benefitted from it...

560
00:18:47,811 --> 00:18:50,740
Are we talking about hair removal or my nickname?

561
00:18:50,741 --> 00:18:52,010
How did we end up talking about hair removal?

562
00:18:52,011 --> 00:18:53,710
- We're talking about everything.
- We're talking about your nickname.

563
00:18:53,711 --> 00:18:54,750
We're talking about the dog that got his stubble removed.

564
00:18:54,751 --> 00:18:56,920
We didn't bring up anything about hair removal.

565
00:18:56,921 --> 00:18:59,491
When you have a chat using the app,

566
00:18:59,721 --> 00:19:01,221
