572
00:19:10,031 --> 00:19:11,701
It became so famous that I even had an autograph event.

573
00:19:11,831 --> 00:19:14,530
- It was actually a very scary role.
- True.

574
00:19:14,531 --> 00:19:17,641
But someone on the internet said I looked like the KakaoTalk Dog.

575
00:19:17,871 --> 00:19:19,540
Whatever I did,

576
00:19:19,541 --> 00:19:21,670
