577
00:19:21,671 --> 00:19:24,040
No matter how scary my role was, it looked cute.

578
00:19:24,041 --> 00:19:25,910
- That's a good thing.
- The image you give.

579
00:19:25,911 --> 00:19:28,080
If you compare that photo to the current him,

580
00:19:28,081 --> 00:19:29,820
- the image is totally different.
- Totally.

581
00:19:29,821 --> 00:19:30,981
Is it because I shaved?

582
00:19:31,021 --> 00:19:32,850
- Next is Gun Woo.
- Gun Woo.

583
00:19:32,851 --> 00:19:34,790
Gun Woo's nickname is Chihuahua.

584
00:19:34,791 --> 00:19:35,850
- Chihuahua?
- But...

585
00:19:35,851 --> 00:19:37,590
- I can see it.
- He does look like one.

586
00:19:37,591 --> 00:19:40,190
These days, I've been constantly told that...

587
00:19:40,191 --> 00:19:41,930
I look like a puppy...

588
00:19:41,931 --> 00:19:43,701
