- A puppy-like face.

589
00:19:43,761 --> 00:19:47,271
Now that I'm in musicals, I get to meet my fans quite often.

590
00:19:47,501 --> 00:19:49,540
They nicknamed me Chihuahua...

591
00:19:49,541 --> 00:19:51,400
and call me Gunhuahua.

592
00:19:51,401 --> 00:19:53,870
- Gunhuahua.
- That's the nickname they gave me.

593
00:19:53,871 --> 00:19:56,011
- I don't know if we look alike.
- Gunhuahua.

594
00:19:56,411 --> 00:19:58,140
That just now looked really scary.

595
00:19:58,141 --> 00:19:59,610
- Hold on.
- Because I was into that character.

596
00:19:59,611 --> 00:20:01,581
Who have you been told you look like the most?

597
00:20:01,881 --> 00:20:02,921
Kwon Oh Joong for me.

598
00:20:03,051 --> 00:20:04,320
Sang Hun is told as Kwon Oh Joong.

599
00:20:04,321 --> 00:20:06,390
- I can totally see Oh Joong.
- Right?

600
00:20:06,391 --> 00:20:10,021
When I was active in Daehangno,

601
00:20:10,321 --> 00:20:12,190
I went to a convenience store,

602
00:20:12,191 --> 00:20:14,791
and a fan gave me a gift.

603
00:20:15,291 --> 00:20:16,600
They said, "I really enjoy your work."

604
00:20:16,601 --> 00:20:19,160
So I thought the fan must've watched my musical.

605
00:20:19,161 --> 00:20:22,000
They asked for my autograph before I left.

606
00:20:22,001 --> 00:20:25,941
I wrote my name under my autograph, "Jeong Sang Hun."

607
00:20:26,101 --> 00:20:28,310
I still can't forget the disappointment...

608
00:20:28,311 --> 00:20:29,810
- in that fan's eyes.
- You still remember it?

609
00:20:29,811 --> 00:20:31,210
- They thought you were Oh Joong.
- The fan expected Kwon Oh Joong.

610
00:20:31,211 --> 00:20:32,810
- Like, "You're not Kwon Oh Joong?"
- Yes.

611
00:20:32,811 --> 00:20:33,950
It's not like they could ask...

612
00:20:33,951 --> 00:20:35,080
- for the gift back.
- Exactly.

613
00:20:35,081 --> 00:20:37,250
- That's when I realized.
- They expected Kwon Oh Joong.

614
00:20:37,251 --> 00:20:39,120
It was when Oh Joong was active.

615
00:20:39,121 --> 00:20:41,090
- You do look alike.
- He was in sitcoms.

616
00:20:41,091 --> 00:20:42,490
Don't we look different now?

617
00:20:42,491 --> 00:20:43,561
What about Sung Rok?

618
00:20:43,821 --> 00:20:45,620
- I'm not sure.
- He doesn't look like anyone.

619
00:20:45,621 --> 00:20:47,761
- Who do I look like? Tell me.
- Just Shin Sung Rok.

620
00:20:47,831 --> 00:20:50,200
Doesn't he look like a comic book character, like Terrius?

621
00:20:50,201 --> 00:20:52,230
- Yes, a similar vibe.
- Listen to the music

622
00:20:52,231 --> 00:20:53,800
- Like a sculpture.
- Yes.

623
00:20:53,801 --> 00:20:55,871
It's just that he's too good-looking.

624
00:20:55,971 --> 00:20:59,840
I've been told several times that I'm musical world's Seo Jang Hoon.

625
00:20:59,841 --> 00:21:00,841
That's not a compliment,

626
00:21:00,841 --> 00:21:01,841
