- His height.

627
00:21:01,842 --> 00:21:02,881
Because I'm tall.

628
00:21:03,181 --> 00:21:04,281
- Because you're tall?
- Because he's tall.

629
00:21:04,481 --> 00:21:07,781
Many actors are close to 190cm tall now.

630
00:21:08,051 --> 00:21:09,380
- If I watch dramas and such.
- The thing is,

631
00:21:09,381 --> 00:21:10,980
there aren't many in the musical world.

632
00:21:10,981 --> 00:21:13,591
There's Min Woo Hyuk. Isn't he close to 190cm?

633
00:21:14,321 --> 00:21:15,950
He's around 186cm or so.

634
00:21:15,951 --> 00:21:19,520
Gosh, that must mean he was wearing thick shoe inserts.

635
00:21:19,521 --> 00:21:20,860
What about Gun Woo?

636
00:21:20,861 --> 00:21:22,931
- A person.
- When I just made my debut...

637
00:21:23,201 --> 00:21:24,700
I feel terrible about it, but I was told...

638
00:21:24,701 --> 00:21:26,160
