680
00:22:51,881 --> 00:22:52,921
- Yes.
- Totally.

681
00:22:53,021 --> 00:22:54,420
A good villain actor is praiseworthy.

682
00:22:54,421 --> 00:22:56,490
- Exactly.
- He acts it out with his heart.

683
00:22:56,491 --> 00:22:58,460
- Not everyone can be a villain.
- Yes.

684
00:22:58,461 --> 00:23:00,190
- For real.
- He's amazing at it.

685
00:23:00,191 --> 00:23:03,160
Gun Woo, is there anyone among us who might play a good villain role?

686
00:23:03,161 --> 00:23:04,301
- Right.
- Like your gut feeling.

687
00:23:04,361 --> 00:23:06,000
I've been wanting to say it since earlier.

688
00:23:06,001 --> 00:23:07,100
- Okay.
- Go ahead.

689
00:23:07,101 --> 00:23:10,301
It's my first time seeing Ho Dong in real life.

690
00:23:11,001 --> 00:23:13,841
And this is my first time meeting someone with such a powerful aura.

691
00:23:17,081 --> 00:23:18,481
- How grotesque.
- For real.

692
00:23:19,541 --> 00:23:20,850
