976
00:32:08,811 --> 00:32:10,010
"I can't bear to see you."

977
00:32:10,011 --> 00:32:11,810
As I was attending school,

978
00:32:11,811 --> 00:32:13,280
I got other opportunities in life.

979
00:32:13,281 --> 00:32:14,751
- "Opportunities?"
- Other opportunities.

980
00:32:14,981 --> 00:32:18,321
Great opportunities that made it hard to focus on school.

981
00:32:18,681 --> 00:32:20,390
- As I got those opportunities...
- He was cast.

982
00:32:20,391 --> 00:32:21,720
Is that what happened?

983
00:32:21,721 --> 00:32:23,250
