992
00:32:36,571 --> 00:32:39,171
- So you didn't like that?
- You didn't like that?

993
00:32:39,341 --> 00:32:40,670
"He's not talented enough."

994
00:32:40,671 --> 00:32:43,740
"Why should I pay this money to learn this?"

995
00:32:43,741 --> 00:32:46,180
- That's what happened.
- He is getting wiped out today.

996
00:32:46,181 --> 00:32:47,310
I get it.

997
00:32:47,311 --> 00:32:49,780
Did you read a lot of "Acting?"

998
00:32:49,781 --> 00:32:50,880
- What?
- "Acting."

999
00:32:50,881 --> 00:32:53,021
