1002
00:32:56,291 --> 00:32:58,790
"Did you take a lot of acting classes?"

1003
00:32:58,791 --> 00:33:00,390
The acting classes.

1004
00:33:00,391 --> 00:33:01,930
Are you asking if he took a lot of acting classes?

1005
00:33:01,931 --> 00:33:04,400
- I didn't understand it.
- Did you take a lot of classes?

1006
00:33:04,401 --> 00:33:07,370
- I didn't get it, either.
- The words were...

1007
00:33:07,371 --> 00:33:09,430
