- I see.

1010
00:33:12,741 --> 00:33:16,340
Did you read "Acting" by Stanislavski?

1011
00:33:16,341 --> 00:33:17,840
Come on, you.

1012
00:33:17,841 --> 00:33:19,440
Come on, you. Be quiet.

1013
00:33:19,441 --> 00:33:21,410
You should have understood it.

1014
00:33:21,411 --> 00:33:23,620
- "Acting" by Stanislavski.
- It's like a textbook.

1015
00:33:23,621 --> 00:33:25,050
Yes, sure.

1016
00:33:25,051 --> 00:33:26,350
I read all of it.

1017
00:33:26,351 --> 00:33:28,990
- Did you study with that, too?
- Sure.

1018
00:33:28,991 --> 00:33:30,660
- You, as well?
- Of course.

1019
