Ji Yeon, who starred with me...

1028
00:33:48,941 --> 00:33:50,840
- in "The Glory."
- Park Yeon Jin?

1029
00:33:50,841 --> 00:33:51,980
- Yes.
- Yeon Jin.

1030
00:33:51,981 --> 00:33:53,850
She heard about that in school...

1031
00:33:53,851 --> 00:33:56,210
