1034
00:33:59,721 --> 00:34:01,090
It was just enough.

1035
00:34:01,091 --> 00:34:04,460
- Really?
- We can tell that...

1036
00:34:04,461 --> 00:34:05,720
even if you don't take your shirt off,

1037
00:34:05,721 --> 00:34:07,190
during the summer,

1038
00:34:07,191 --> 00:34:08,460
when you have a shirt on,

1039
00:34:08,461 --> 00:34:11,130
- we can just see it.
- It looks different.

