- We learned about him.
- Dr. Yu Il Han.

1057
00:34:47,201 --> 00:34:49,100
- We learned it.
- We studied history.

1058
00:34:49,101 --> 00:34:51,370
He donated his entire assets to the independence fund.

1059
00:34:51,371 --> 00:34:52,371
That's right.

1060
00:34:52,372 --> 00:34:56,041
(They learned about Dr. Yu during Teacher Big Star's lesson.)

1061
00:34:56,511 --> 00:34:57,641
(During the Japanese colonial period, )

1062
00:34:58,111 --> 00:34:59,811
(the people living on the Korean Peninsula...)

1063
