1082
00:35:48,131 --> 00:35:50,130
(A spy agency and special operations formed by the U.S. Army and Navy)

1083
00:35:50,131 --> 00:35:52,930
- They had the Napko Project, - Yes.

1084
00:35:52,931 --> 00:35:55,330
and during the early 1990s,

1085
00:35:55,331 --> 00:35:58,100
