1092
00:36:09,511 --> 00:36:12,020
He had never told anyone his whole life.

1093
00:36:12,021 --> 00:36:16,451
The more you think of it, he's amazing because Dr. Yu...

1094
00:36:16,751 --> 00:36:19,590
established a company for the health...

1095
00:36:19,591 --> 00:36:21,360
