He must have been busy,

1100
00:36:28,931 --> 00:36:32,201
but he also worked as a spy.

1101
00:36:32,301 --> 00:36:33,440
- Even the independence movement.
- He's really...

1102
00:36:33,441 --> 00:36:34,441
- He's an incredible person.
