- Canned...

1108
00:36:43,411 --> 00:36:44,421
- What?
- That's right.

1109
00:36:45,181 --> 00:36:46,850
- Bean sprouts.
- Yes.

1110
00:36:46,851 --> 00:36:48,290
It was sold to the Chinese.

1111
00:36:48,291 --> 00:36:49,550
- Yes.
- He studied it all.

